WEBVTT

00:09:28.157 --> 00:09:32.307
I started to understand

00:09:32.331 --> 00:09:35.465
what leadership really means.

00:09:35.832 --> 00:09:39.308
So I decided to go back to my region

00:09:39.332 --> 00:09:43.382
and take a position as a teacher
in a remote school,

00:09:44.204 --> 00:09:48.490
a school that I have to reach by bus --

00:09:48.514 --> 00:09:53.235
two hours traveling,
every morning and evening.

00:09:53.768 --> 00:09:58.355
Though it was hard, on my first day I knew

00:09:58.379 --> 00:10:00.929
I made the right decision.